description: The SPDR MSCI ACWI ex-US ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the total return performance of the MSCI ACWI ex USA Index (the “Index”)Seeks to provide access to virtually all developed and emerging market countries outside of the USThe Index provides a broad measure of stock performance covering approximately 85% of the global equity opportunity set outside the USSeeks to provide large and mid cap security exposure using a market-cap weighted index methodology
name: SPDR MSCI ACWI ex-US ETF
